blog.name: askspiderbite
blog.title: SpiderBite
blog.description:
Ask and you shall receive. Questions for SpiderBite (PeterxGwen) and company are welcome.
Ask box is open to questions

body:
Stake Out

(Tony walks up to and sits down at a table outside a small pizzeria in downtown New York.)

Tony: Hello, Mr. Leeds…

(Ned, wearing a fake mustache and glasses, pops up from behind a Daily Bugle.)

Ned: tOnY sTaRk!!?!?!!???!😨

Tony: and Ms. Watson.

(MJ, not behind the newspaper, simply makes an acknowledging hand gesture without looking up from her phone.)

MJ: ‘Sup.😑

Tony: I assume we’re all here for the same reason? Either way, I’m ordering something.

(He waves over a waitress and orders an item off the lunch menu.)

Tony: So, how’s Peter doing on his little date?

Ned: uHh, He….. UhHh. UmMmM…😨

MJ: They’ve been here for about an hour. They ordered a medium pizza to share; he paid.

(Peter and Gwen chat as they eat four tables down from Ned, MJ, and Tony.)

Tony: Well, it seems he’s doing well so far. Let’s see if he can stick the landing.

MJ: Shouldn’t you be off avenging something or someone, or being a billionaire? Why are you stalking your little sidekick on his date?

Tony: I could ask the same thing, Ms. Watson.

MJ: Fair enough.😑

Ned: SSSHHHHHH, I think they heard us.🤫😬

(Four tables down…)

Gwen: Are they spying on us?

Peter: That is Ned’s spy mustache.🤔

______________________________________________

Send in questions if you have them, whomever you ask will answer as well as they can.

summary: I just had a thought! In Spider-Man: Far From Home, Fury says “nice to finally meet you.” I saw some people talking about how it...
body:
I just had a thought! In Spider-Man: Far From Home, Fury says “nice to finally meet you.” I saw some people talking about how it was Tony blocking Fury all these years, but then I remembered something…

Nick Fury is the one that recruited Richard Parker -AKA, Peter’s dad- to join the CIA! What if Fury had been keeping an eye on Peter all these years???
